data.description:
3 bedroom 3 bathroom home with a loft and 2 car garage. End unit with screened in porch and fenced in private yard. Home is in a gated community with 24 security guard. Community center with pool, basketball courts, and workout room. Upstairs guest bathroom has been renovated and brand new carpet on stairs. Close to shopping and restaurants.

Water and cable included in rent. Pets are allowed however must be approved by neighborhood HOA. 12 month lease only. First, last, and security deposit required.
